examples: A futuristic robot with sleek metallic design.
prompt.title: Prompt
prompt.description: A textual prompt to guide model generation. Required for Text-to-3D mode. Optional for Image-to-3D mode.

condition_mode.title: Condition Mode
condition_mode.description: For fuse mode, One or more images are required.It will generate a model by extracting and fusing features of objects from multiple images.For concat mode, need to upload multiple multi-view images of the same object and generate the model. (You can upload multi-view images in any order, regardless of the order of view.)

bbox_condition.title: Bbox Condition
bbox_condition.description: An array that specifies the dimensions and scaling factor of the bounding box. Typically, this array contains 3 elements, Length(X-axis), Width(Y-axis) and Height(Z-axis).

tier.title: Tier
tier.description: Tier of generation. For Rodin Sketch, set to Sketch. For Rodin Regular, set to Regular.

quality.title: Quality
quality.description: Generation quality. Possible values: high, medium, low, extra-low. Default is medium.

TAPose.title: T/A Pose
TAPose.description: When generating the human-like model, this parameter control the generation result to T/A Pose.

input_image_urls.title: Input Image Urls
input_image_urls.description: URL of images to use while generating the 3D model. Required for Image-to-3D mode. Optional for Text-to-3D mode.

geometry_file_format.title: Geometry File Format
geometry_file_format.description: Format of the geometry file. Possible values: glb, usdz, fbx, obj, stl. Default is glb.

use_hyper.title: Use Hyper
use_hyper.description: Whether to export the model using hyper mode. Default is false.

addons.title: Addons
addons.description: Generation add-on features. Default is []. Possible values are HighPack. The HighPack option will provide 4K resolution textures instead of the default 1K, as well as models with high-poly. It will cost triple the billable units.

seed.title: Seed
seed.description: Seed value for randomization, ranging from 0 to 65535. Optional.

material.title: Material
material.description: Material type. Possible values: PBR, Shaded. Default is PBR.
